text: Störmecke is a locality in the municipality Schmallenberg in the district Hochsauerlandkreis in North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany. The hamlet has 3 inhabitantsSchmallenberg.de: Inhabitants and located almost seven kilometres southeast of the Schmallenberg city centre. Störmecke borders on the villages of Latrop, Schanze, Grafschaft and Kühhude. ==References== Category:Villages in North Rhine-Westphalia Category:Schmallenberg
